Bossy McBossFace's First mate is a skeleton that can spawn during the fight with Bossy McBossFace. Bossy will on occasion spawn a number of summoned skeletons, this group of skeletons may include the first mate.

Achievement[edit | edit source]

  • Monkey Sadness ( 5) – Defeat Bossy McBossface's first mate.

Update history[edit | edit source]

This information has been compiled as part of the update history project. Some updates may not be included – see here for how to help out!
  • update 25 February 2019 (Update):
    • Added to game.

Trivia[edit | edit source]

  • Its examine text is a pun on "primate".
